articles.title: Cannes: Palme d'Or Winner 'Anora,' Jesse Plemons Get Oscar Boost - IndieWire
articles.description: At the 2024 Cannes Film Festival, Palme d'Or winner 'Anora' and Best Actor winner Jesse Plemons Get an Oscars boost.
